name: Johns Hopkins Diabetes Guide (via uCentral) (Unbound Medicine)
description: The Johns Hopkins Diabetes Guide puts an in-depth resource focused solely on the management of diabetes and associated conditions in an integrated application for use on the web or mobile devices. Explore the evidence-based specifics of diabetes complication all with the most up-to-date diagnostic and treatment recommendations. The Johns Hopkins Diabetes Guide also includes how-to details of clinical testing and medications.
